sub_title: Lead Strategy & Business | The Icon Hub | Swedish/Polish | Influencer & Social Media fluent | EX-Mediamonks
summary:
Experienced Influencer Marketing Professional | Team Leader | Account Manager

I am a results-oriented and dynamic influencer marketing professional with a strong track record of success in leading teams and delivering impactful campaigns. With a passion for creating iconic connections, I have consistently driven business growth and fostered long-lasting relationships with clients.

Currently, as the Lead of Strategy & Business at The Icon Hub, I am responsible for overseeing all aspects of influencer strategy and business development. By implementing data-driven approaches and leveraging tools like CIQ, I ensure seamless project execution and empower the team to achieve exceptional results.

Prior to this, I served as the Influencer Strategy Team Lead at MediaMonks, where I successfully guided cross-functional teams in executing influencer campaigns for renowned brands. I also gained valuable experience as the Influencer Development Team Lead at IMA Influencer Marketing Agency, where I honed my expertise in team management and organization skills.

Throughout my career, I have consistently demonstrated a strong ability to navigate the ever-evolving influencer landscape. My proficiency in account management has allowed me to build and nurture strategic partnerships, resulting in increased client satisfaction and business growth.

With a Master's degree in Marketing from Vrije Universiteit Amsterdam, I possess a solid academic foundation that complements my practical industry knowledge. I am fluent in English, Polish, and Swedish, which enables effective communication and collaboration in diverse international environments.

If you are seeking a dedicated professional who can drive your influencer marketing initiatives to new heights, let's connect. I am always open to exploring opportunities that allow me to leverage my skills and contribute to the success of forward-thinking organizations.
